## 🛠 Setup

### 1. Create Virtual Environment

#### 🐧 Linux / 🍎 macOS:

```sh
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
```

#### 🪟 Window:

```sh
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```sh
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

